name: ObesityChecker
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: obesity checker
des:
Saying your height and weight, you can see your BMI value and suitable weight.
Say your height in centimeters and your bodyweight in kilograms.

How to invocate: Alexa, open obesity checker
How to say weight (example): 65 kg, weight 65 kg
How to say height (example): 170 cm, height 170 cm

"The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
